trans-unit.source: This interface represents a collection of <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.Bootstrapper.Product> objects.

The collection is a closed set that is generated by the <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.Bootstrapper.BootstrapperBuilder> based on the <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.Bootstrapper.BootstrapperBuilder.Path%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: 该集合是由生成的封闭的集<xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.Bootstrapper.BootstrapperBuilder>基于<xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.Bootstrapper.BootstrapperBuilder.Path%2A>属性。</xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.Bootstrapper.BootstrapperBuilder.Path%2A> </xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.Bootstrapper.BootstrapperBuilder>

trans-unit.source: The client cannot add or remove items from this collection.
trans-unit.target: 客户端无法添加或移除此集合中的项。

trans-unit.source: Gets the number of elements that are contained in the product collection.
trans-unit.target: 获取产品集合中包含的元素的数目。

trans-unit.source: The number of elements that are contained in the product collection.
trans-unit.target: 产品集合中包含的元素数目。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the product at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: 检索位于指定索引处的产品。

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index of the element to get.
trans-unit.target: 要获取的元素的从零开始的索引。

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.Bootstrapper.Product"></xref> object at the specified index.
Retrieves the product with the specified product code.
trans-unit.target: 检索具有指定的产品代码的产品。

trans-unit.source: The unique identifier of the product to get.
trans-unit.target: 要获取的产品的唯一标识符。

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.Bootstrapper.Product"></xref> object that has the specified product code; null if the specified product code is not found.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.Bootstrapper.Product"> </xref>具有指定的产品代码; 如果找不到指定的产品代码则为 null 的对象。
